{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Defend your farm</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A relaxing day at the farm. But what is this? Where does this rat come from? Kitty grabs a fish and after a few throws... the rat is gone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3525680/extras/KittyShooting.gif?t=1739394263\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Get stronger</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More enemies are approaching, but Kitty is improving, too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3525680/extras/CardSelection.gif?t=1739394263\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlock Skills</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And Kitty isn\u2019t alone! Recruit other animals from the farm, like Stompy the bull, to join the fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3525680/extras/Stompy.gif?t=1739394263\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Permanent Upgrades (Not available in the demo)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The farm didn\u2019t hold. Let\u2019s give it another try, but this time with some upgrades. Kitty collected enough daisies to unlock improvements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3525680/extras/Upgrades.gif?t=1739394263\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlock Characters (Not available in the demo)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maybe a friend can help? Let\u2019s defend the farm with Fluffy, the electrifying sheep!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps